Concatenate One or More Quosure(s)

Source: R/quo.R
dev_util_quo_c.Rd

Concatenate One or More Quosure(s)

quo_c(...)

Arguments

...

One or more objects of class quosure or quosures

Value

An object of class quosures

Author

Thomas Neitmann

Examples

admiral:::quo_c(rlang::quo(USUBJID))
#> <list_of<quosure>>
#> 
#> [[1]]
#> <quosure>
#> expr: ^USUBJID
#> env:  0x56520545faa8
#> 
admiral:::quo_c(rlang::quo(STUDYID), rlang::quo(USUBJID))
#> <list_of<quosure>>
#> 
#> [[1]]
#> <quosure>
#> expr: ^STUDYID
#> env:  0x56520545faa8
#> 
#> [[2]]
#> <quosure>
#> expr: ^USUBJID
#> env:  0x56520545faa8
#> 
admiral:::quo_c(vars(USUBJID, ADTM))
#> <list_of<quosure>>
#> 
#> [[1]]
#> <quosure>
#> expr: ^USUBJID
#> env:  0x56520545faa8
#> 
#> [[2]]
#> <quosure>
#> expr: ^ADTM
#> env:  0x56520545faa8
#> 
admiral:::quo_c(rlang::quo(BASETYPE), vars(USUBJID, PARAM), rlang::quo(ADTM))
#> <list_of<quosure>>
#> 
#> [[1]]
#> <quosure>
#> expr: ^BASETYPE
#> env:  0x56520545faa8
#> 
#> [[2]]
#> <quosure>
#> expr: ^USUBJID
#> env:  0x56520545faa8
#> 
#> [[3]]
#> <quosure>
#> expr: ^PARAM
#> env:  0x56520545faa8
#> 
#> [[4]]
#> <quosure>
#> expr: ^ADTM
#> env:  0x56520545faa8
#>
